    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，ActuatorController作为起点。那PLC Logic放在什么位置？是和ActuatorController并列还是嵌套关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
