    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "PLC Logic应该和ActuatorController有双向关系，但实际上我画的是从ActuatorController指向PLC Logic，同时PLC Logic还要分出两条线：一条连到它自己形成闭环，另一条连到EdgeNode。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以PLC Logic有自环，同时连接一个EdgeNode。MQTT Broker那边呢？",
