    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "前面PLC Logic分出来的那两个节点，AA和AB，也要连到E。AA是自环的那个PLC Logic，AB是EdgeNode。",
