      "utterance": "确认一下：AA是PLC Logic的自环节点，AB是EdgeNode，两者都指向Broker E。这样E就有四个入边了：C、D、AA、AB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
